# 4. ✅ Get OpenAI API key and set OPENAI_API_KEY
# 5. ✅ Update all security secrets (APP_SECRET, JWT_SECRET, etc.)
# 6. ⬜ Configure email service (SendGrid recommended)
# 7. ⬜ Set up cloud storage (AWS S3 recommended)
# 8. ⬜ Configure monitoring (Sentry recommended)
# 9. ⬜ Enable desired integrations (ATS, translation, etc.)
# 10. ⬜ Update business configuration as needed

# =============================================================================
# MINIMAL CONFIGURATION FOR DEVELOPMENT
# =============================================================================
# For a minimal development setup, you only need:
# - DATABASE_URL (PostgreSQL)
# - REDIS_URL (Redis)
# - OPENAI_API_KEY (OpenAI)
# - Update all *_SECRET variables
